	        <tr>
			  <td colspan=3 valign="top">
		          <span class=msg>
				   There are probably special-use cases where raid 0 would help.  I'm thinking rendering tens to hundreds of gigabytes of video in Adobe Premier or something like that.  Other than that I agree it's probably not going to help most people.  By most I mean 99.999%. 
					<span class="info"></span>
					 <br><br>_____________________________<br><br><div align="center"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=181972">Parm Vomgrossenhirn</a> - Coercer<i> <br> ** Will Mez for Food **</i></div> 
				  
				  </span>
	          </td>
	        </tr>
		  </table>
